@@TJvGenetic.NewGeneration
Description:
Call this method when you want to start a new generation. All old members are freed. You have to call this method before to call the NextGeneration one. You also have to call this method after a modification of the MemberSize or Numbers of Members. The event ONTestMember is called each time a new member has been generated.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvGenetic.NextGeneration
Description:
Call this method when you want to go to the next generation. All old members are replaced by new ones. The event ONTestMember is calld each time a new member has been generated.

